OL,6,FShe said: "We are delighted that,
OL,7,Fthanks to the combined efforts of FTWW
OL,8,Fand our members, signatories to our
OL,9,FSenedd petition, Sioned Williams MS,
OL,10,Fand ITV Wales, this year's Adenomyosis
OL,11,FAwareness Month has been a successful
OL,12,Fone for patients in Wales, with the
OL,13,Fcabinet secretary for health and
OL,14,Fsocial care reacting promptly and
OL,15,Fdecisively in ensuring that
OL,16,Fadenomyosis is added to the NHS Wales
OL,17,F111 A-Z.
