OL,6,F"There are many thousands of patients
OL,7,Facross Wales struggling with symptoms
OL,8,Fof adenomyosis, a condition more
OL,9,Fcommon than diabetes or asthma in
OL,10,Fwomen and which, until last week, had
OL,11,Fscant attention paid to it.
