OL,6,F"Whilst a small step in improving
OL,7,Fwider understanding and treatment,
OL,8,Fensuring that trusted information
OL,9,Fabout the condition is available on a
OL,10,Fsite as well-known and frequented as
OL,11,Fthe NHS Wales 111 A-Z is absolutely a
OL,12,Fmove in the right direction,
OL,13,Fdemonstrating that women's voices are
OL,14,Findeed being heard by the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment as it sets about developing
OL,16,Fits 10-year women's health plan."
OL,18,FWales' health secretary Eluned Morgan
OL,19,Fsaid: "I'm pleased to be able to help
OL,20,Fin any way to raise awareness of
OL,21,Fadenomyosis.
