OL,3,CAdenomyosis officially recognised by
OL,4,CNHS Wales after ITV Cymru Wales report
OL,6,F"Like many other debilitating
OL,7,Fconditions that affect women, it
OL,8,Fhasn't had the attention it should
OL,9,Fhave.
OL,11,F"I am determined to do what I can to
OL,12,Ftackle the historical bias against
OL,13,Fwomen's health conditions.
OL,15,F"This includes recently appointing the
OL,16,Ffirst ever clinical lead for women's
OL,17,Fhealth in Wales, who will lead the
OL,18,Fdevelopment of a new plan to improve
OL,19,Fservices."
